&lt;h2 id="visualizing-the-ai-automation-workflow"&gt;Visualizing the AI Automation Workflow&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To better understand how these strategies can be implemented, here’s a simple workflow diagram illustrating the process of integrating AI automation into your small business:&lt;/p&gt;
